36enum cv8_symheadtype {
37 CV8_DEBUG_SYMS = 0xF1, /* CV5 symbol information */
38 CV8_LINE_NUMS = 0xF2, /* line numbers for a section */
39 CV8_FILE_STRTAB = 0xF3, /* filename string table */
40 CV8_FILE_INFO = 0xF4 /* source file info */
41};
42
43enum cv_symtype {
44 /* Non-modal Symbols */
45 CV_S_COMPILE = 0x0001, /* Compile Flag */
46 CV_S_REGISTER = 0x0002, /* Register */
47 CV_S_CONSTANT = 0x0003, /* Constant */
48 CV_S_UDT = 0x0004, /* User-defined Type */
49 CV_S_SSEARCH = 0x0005, /* Start Search */
50 CV_S_END = 0x0006, /* End of Block */
51 CV_S_SKIP = 0x0007, /* Skip Record */
52 CV_S_OBJNAME = 0x0009, /* Object File Name */
53 CV_S_ENDARG = 0x000a, /* End of Arguments */
54 CV_S_COBOLUDT = 0x000b, /* COBOL User-defined Type */
55 CV_S_MANYREG = 0x000c, /* Many Registers */
56 CV_S_RETURN = 0x000d, /* Function Return */
57 CV_S_ENTRYTHIS = 0x000e, /* "this" at Method Entry */
58
59 /* Symbols for 16:16 Segmented Architectures */
60 CV_S_BPREL16 = 0x0100, /* BP Relative 16:16 */
61 CV_S_LDATA16 = 0x0101, /* Local Data 16:16 */
62 CV_S_GDATA16 = 0x0102, /* Global Data Symbol 16:16 */
63 CV_S_PUB16 = 0x0103, /* Public Symbol 16:16 */
64 CV_S_LPROC16 = 0x0104, /* Local Start 16:16 */
65 CV_S_GPROC16 = 0x0105, /* Global Start 16:16 */
66 CV_S_THUNK16 = 0x0106, /* Thunk Start 16:16 */
67 CV_S_BLOCK16 = 0x0107, /* Block Start 16:16 */
68 CV_S_WITH16 = 0x0108, /* With Start 16:16 */
69 CV_S_LABEL16 = 0x0109, /* Code Label 16:16 */
70 CV_S_CEXMODEL16 = 0x0110, /* Change Execution Model 16:16 */
71 CV_S_VFTPATH16 = 0x010b, /* Virtual Function Table Path 16:16 */
72 CV_S_REGREL16 = 0x010c, /* Register Relative 16:16 */
73
74 /* Symbols for 16:32 Segmented Architectures */
75 CV_S_BPREL32 = 0x0200, /* BP Relative 16:32 */
76 CV_S_LDATA32 = 0x0201, /* Local Data 16:32 */
77 CV_S_GDATA32 = 0x0202, /* Global Data Symbol 16:32 */
78 CV_S_PUB32 = 0x0203, /* Public Symbol 16:32 */
79 CV_S_LPROC32 = 0x0204, /* Local Start 16:32 */
80 CV_S_GPROC32 = 0x0205, /* Global Start 16:32 */
81 CV_S_THUNK32 = 0x0206, /* Thunk Start 16:32 */
82 CV_S_BLOCK32 = 0x0207, /* Block Start 16:32 */
83 CV_S_WITH32 = 0x0208, /* With Start 16:32 */
84 CV_S_LABEL32 = 0x0209, /* Code Label 16:32 */
85 CV_S_CEXMODEL32 = 0x0210, /* Change Execution Model 16:32 */
86 CV_S_VFTPATH32 = 0x020b, /* Virtual Function Table Path 16:32 */
87 CV_S_REGREL32 = 0x020c, /* Register Relative 16:32 */
88 CV_S_LTHREAD32 = 0x020d, /* Local Thread Storage 16:32 */
89 CV_S_GTHREAD32 = 0x020e, /* Global Thread Storage 16:32 */
90
91 /* Symbols for MIPS */
92 CV_S_LPROCMIPS = 0x0300, /* Local procedure start MIPS */
93 CV_S_GPROCMIPS = 0x0301, /* Global procedure start MIPS */
94
95 /* Symbols for CV8 - strings are 0 terminated rather than length-prefix.
96 * Incomplete and unofficial.
97 */
98 CV8_S_OBJNAME = 0x1101, /* Object File Name */
99 CV8_S_LABEL32 = 0x1105, /* Code Label 16:32 */
100 CV8_S_LDATA32 = 0x110c, /* Local Data 16:32 */
101 CV8_S_GDATA32 = 0x110d, /* Global Data 16:32 */
102 CV8_S_LPROC32 = 0x1110, /* Local Start 16:32 */
103 CV8_S_COMPILE = 0x1116 /* Compile Flag */
104};

106typedef struct cv8_symhead {
107 enum cv8_symheadtype type;
108 yasm_bytecode *start_prevbc;
109 yasm_bytecode *end_prevbc;
110 int first; /* nonzero if first symhead in section */
111} cv8_symhead;

113typedef struct cv8_fileinfo {
114 const cv_filename *fn;
115} cv8_fileinfo;

117/* Note: each line number group is associated with a file AND a section */
118typedef struct cv8_linepair {
119 unsigned long offset;
120 unsigned long line;
121} cv8_linepair;
122
123/* Decrease linked list overhead a bit doing it this way */
124typedef struct cv8_lineset {
125 STAILQ_ENTRY(cv8_lineset) link;
126 cv8_linepair pairs[126];
127 size_t num_pairs;
128} cv8_lineset;
129
130/* Note: Due to line number sorting requirements (by section offset it seems)
131 * one file may need more than one record per section. */
132typedef struct cv8_lineinfo {
133 STAILQ_ENTRY(cv8_lineinfo) link;
134 const cv_filename *fn; /* filename associated with line numbers */
135 yasm_section *sect; /* section line numbers are for */
136 yasm_symrec *sectsym; /* symbol for beginning of sect */
137 unsigned long num_linenums;
138 int first_in_sect; /* First lineinfo for this section. */
139 STAILQ_HEAD(cv8_lineset_head, cv8_lineset) linesets;
140} cv8_lineinfo;
141
142/* Symbols use a bit of meta-programming to encode formats: each character
143 * of format represents the output generated, as follows:
144 * 'b' : 1 byte value (integer)
145 * 'h' : 2 byte value (integer)
146 * 'w' : 4 byte value (integer)
147 * 'Y' : symrec SECREL+SECTION (pointer)
148 * 'T' : type index (integer)
149 * 'S' : length-prefixed string (pointer)
150 * 'Z' : 0-terminated string (pointer)
151 */
152typedef struct cv_sym {
153 enum cv_symtype type;
154 const char *format;
155 union {
156 unsigned long i;
157 void *p;
158 } args[10];
159} cv_sym;

256static cv_sym *
257cv8_add_sym_objname(yasm_section *sect, /*@keep@*/ char *objname)
258{
259 yasm_bytecode *bc;
260 cv_sym *cvs = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv_sym));
261 cvs->type = CV8_S_OBJNAME;
262 cvs->format = "wZ";
263 cvs->args[0].i = 0; /* signature (0=asm) */
264 cvs->args[1].p = objname; /* object filename */
265
266 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv_sym_bc_callback, cvs, 0);
267 bc->len = cv_sym_size(cvs);
268 yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc);
269 return cvs;
270}
271
272static cv_sym *
273cv8_add_sym_compile(yasm_object *object, yasm_section *sect,
274 /*@keep@*/ char *creator)
275{
276 yasm_bytecode *bc;
277 cv_sym *cvs = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv_sym));
278 cvs->type = CV8_S_COMPILE;
279 cvs->format = "wwwwZh";
280 cvs->args[0].i = 3; /* language (3=Masm) */
281
282 /* target processor; 0xD0 = AMD64 */
283 if (strcmp(yasm_arch_keyword(object->arch), "x86") == 0) {
284 if (strcmp(yasm_arch_get_machine(object->arch), "amd64") == 0)
285 cvs->args[1].i = 0xD0;
286 else
287 cvs->args[1].i = 0x6; /* 686, FIXME */
288 } else
289 cvs->args[1].i = 0; /* XXX: unknown */
290
291 cvs->args[2].i = 0; /* flags (assume 0 for now) */
292 cvs->args[3].i = 0; /* creator version number (assume 0 for now) */
293 cvs->args[4].p = creator; /* creator string */
294 cvs->args[5].i = 0; /* no pairs of key/value */
295
296 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv_sym_bc_callback, cvs, 0);
297 bc->len = cv_sym_size(cvs);
298 yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc);
299 return cvs;
300}
301
302static cv_sym *
303cv8_add_sym_label(yasm_section *sect, yasm_symrec *sym)
304{
305 yasm_bytecode *bc;
306 cv_sym *cvs = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv_sym));
307 cvs->type = CV8_S_LABEL32;
308 cvs->format = "YbZ";
309 cvs->args[0].p = sym; /* symrec for label */
310 cvs->args[1].i = 0; /* flags (assume 0 for now) */
311 cvs->args[2].p = yasm__xstrdup(yasm_symrec_get_name(sym));
312
313 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv_sym_bc_callback, cvs, 0);
314 bc->len = cv_sym_size(cvs);
315 yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc);
316 return cvs;
317}
318
319static cv_sym *
320cv8_add_sym_data(yasm_section *sect, unsigned long type, yasm_symrec *sym,
321 int is_global)
322{
323 yasm_bytecode *bc;
324 cv_sym *cvs = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv_sym));
325 cvs->type = is_global ? CV8_S_GDATA32 : CV8_S_LDATA32;
326 cvs->format = "wYZ";
327 cvs->args[0].i = type; /* type index */
328 cvs->args[1].p = sym; /* symrec for label */
329 cvs->args[2].p = yasm__xstrdup(yasm_symrec_get_name(sym));
330
331 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv_sym_bc_callback, cvs, 0);
332 bc->len = cv_sym_size(cvs);
333 yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc);
334 return cvs;
335}

337static size_t
338cv_dbgfmt_add_file(yasm_dbgfmt_cv *dbgfmt_cv, size_t filenum,
339 const char *filename)
340{
341 char *pathname;
342 size_t i;
343 yasm_md5_context context;
344 FILE *f;
345 unsigned char *buf;
346 size_t len;
347
348 /* Put the filename into the filename table */
349 if (filenum == 0) {
350 /* Look to see if we already have that filename in the table */
351 for (; filenum<dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size; filenum++) {
352 if (!dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].filename ||
353 strcmp(dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].filename, filename) == 0)
354 break;
355 }
356 } else
357 filenum--; /* array index is 0-based */
358
359 /* Realloc table if necessary */
360 if (filenum >= dbgfmt_cv->filenames_allocated) {
361 size_t old_allocated = dbgfmt_cv->filenames_allocated;
362 dbgfmt_cv->filenames_allocated = filenum+32;
363 dbgfmt_cv->filenames = yasm_xrealloc(dbgfmt_cv->filenames,
364 sizeof(cv_filename)*dbgfmt_cv->filenames_allocated);
365 for (i=old_allocated; i<dbgfmt_cv->filenames_allocated; i++) {
366 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].pathname = NULL;
367 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].filename = NULL;
368 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].str_off = 0;
369 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].info_off = 0;
370 }
371 }
372
373 /* Calculate MD5 checksum of file */
374 buf = yasm_xmalloc(1024);
375 yasm_md5_init(&context);
376 f = fopen(filename, "rb");
377 if (!f)
378 yasm__fatal(N_("codeview: could not open source file"));
379 while ((len = fread(buf, 1, 1024, f)) > 0)
380 yasm_md5_update(&context, buf, (unsigned long)len);
381 yasm_md5_final(dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].digest, &context);
382 fclose(f);
383 yasm_xfree(buf);
384
385 /* Actually save in table */
386 if (dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].pathname)
387 yasm_xfree(dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].pathname);
388 if (dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].filename)
389 yasm_xfree(dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].filename);
390
391 pathname = yasm__abspath(filename);
392 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].pathname = pathname;
393 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[filenum].filename = yasm__xstrdup(filename);
394
395 /* Update table size */
396 if (filenum >= dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size)
397 dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size = filenum + 1;
398
399 return filenum;
400}
401
402static yasm_bytecode *
403cv_append_str(yasm_section *sect, const char *str)
404{
405 yasm_datavalhead dvs;
406 yasm_bytecode *bc;
407
408 yasm_dvs_initialize(&dvs);
409 yasm_dvs_append(&dvs, yasm_dv_create_string(yasm__xstrdup(str),
410 strlen(str)));
411 bc = yasm_bc_create_data(&dvs, 1, 1, NULL, 0);
412 yasm_bc_finalize(bc, yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc));
413 yasm_bc_calc_len(bc, NULL, NULL);
414 return bc;
415}

417typedef struct cv_line_info {
418 yasm_section *debug_symline;
419 yasm_object *object;
420 yasm_dbgfmt_cv *dbgfmt_cv;
421 yasm_linemap *linemap;
422 yasm_errwarns *errwarns;
423 unsigned int num_lineinfos;
424 STAILQ_HEAD(cv8_lineinfo_head, cv8_lineinfo) cv8_lineinfos;
425 /*@null@*/ cv8_lineinfo *cv8_cur_li;
426 /*@null@*/ cv8_lineset *cv8_cur_ls;
427} cv_line_info;
428
429static int
430cv_generate_line_bc(yasm_bytecode *bc, /*@null@*/ void *d)
431{
432 cv_line_info *info = (cv_line_info *)d;
433 yasm_dbgfmt_cv *dbgfmt_cv = info->dbgfmt_cv;
434 size_t i;
435 const char *filename;
436 unsigned long line;
437 /*@null@*/ yasm_bytecode *nextbc = yasm_bc__next(bc);
438 yasm_section *sect = yasm_bc_get_section(bc);
439
440 if (nextbc && bc->offset == nextbc->offset)
441 return 0;
442
443 yasm_linemap_lookup(info->linemap, bc->line, &filename, &line);
444
445 if (!info->cv8_cur_li
446 || strcmp(filename, info->cv8_cur_li->fn->filename) != 0) {
447 yasm_bytecode *sectbc;
448 char symname[8];
449 int first_in_sect = !info->cv8_cur_li;
450
451 /* Find file */
452 for (i=0; i<dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size; i++) {
453 if (strcmp(filename, dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].filename) == 0)
454 break;
455 }
456 if (i >= dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size)
457 yasm_internal_error(N_("could not find filename in table"));
458
459 /* and create new lineinfo structure */
460 info->cv8_cur_li = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv8_lineinfo));
461 info->cv8_cur_li->fn = &dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i];
462 info->cv8_cur_li->sect = sect;
463 info->cv8_cur_li->first_in_sect = first_in_sect;
464 sectbc = yasm_section_bcs_first(sect);
465 if (sectbc->symrecs && sectbc->symrecs[0])
466 info->cv8_cur_li->sectsym = sectbc->symrecs[0];
467 else {
468 sprintf(symname, ".%06u", info->num_lineinfos++);
469 info->cv8_cur_li->sectsym =
470 yasm_symtab_define_label(info->object->symtab, symname, sectbc,
471 1, 0);
472 }
473 info->cv8_cur_li->num_linenums = 0;
474 STAILQ_INIT(&info->cv8_cur_li->linesets);
475 STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL(&info->cv8_lineinfos, info->cv8_cur_li, link);
476 info->cv8_cur_ls = NULL;
477 }
478
479 /* build new lineset if necessary */
480 if (!info->cv8_cur_ls || info->cv8_cur_ls->num_pairs >= 126) {
481 info->cv8_cur_ls = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv8_lineset));
482 info->cv8_cur_ls->num_pairs = 0;
483 STAILQ_INSERT_TAIL(&info->cv8_cur_li->linesets, info->cv8_cur_ls, link);
484 }
485
486 /* add linepair for this bytecode */
487 info->cv8_cur_ls->pairs[info->cv8_cur_ls->num_pairs].offset = bc->offset;
488 info->cv8_cur_ls->pairs[info->cv8_cur_ls->num_pairs].line =
489 0x80000000 | line;
490 info->cv8_cur_ls->num_pairs++;
491 info->cv8_cur_li->num_linenums++;
492
493 return 0;
494}
495
496static int
497cv_generate_line_section(yasm_section *sect, /*@null@*/ void *d)
498{
499 cv_line_info *info = (cv_line_info *)d;
500
501 if (!yasm_section_is_code(sect))
502 return 0; /* not code, so no line data for this section */
503
504 info->cv8_cur_li = NULL;
505 info->cv8_cur_ls = NULL;
506
507 yasm_section_bcs_traverse(sect, info->errwarns, info, cv_generate_line_bc);
508
509 return 0;
510}
511
512static int
513cv_generate_filename(const char *filename, void *d)
514{
515 cv_dbgfmt_add_file((yasm_dbgfmt_cv *)d, 0, filename);
516 return 0;
517}
518
519static int
520cv_generate_sym(yasm_symrec *sym, void *d)
521{
522 cv_line_info *info = (cv_line_info *)d;
523 yasm_bytecode *precbc;
524 const char *name = yasm_symrec_get_name(sym);
525
526 /* only care about labels (for now). Don't put in symbols starting with
527 * ".", as these are typically internally generated ones (like section
528 * symbols).
529 */
530 if (name[0] == '.' || !yasm_symrec_get_label(sym, &precbc))
531 return 0;
532
533 /* TODO: add data types; until then, just mark everything as UBYTE */
534 if (yasm_section_is_code(yasm_bc_get_section(precbc)))
535 cv8_add_sym_label(info->debug_symline, sym);
536 else
537 cv8_add_sym_data(info->debug_symline, 0x20, sym,
538 yasm_symrec_get_visibility(sym) & YASM_SYM_GLOBAL?1:0);
539 return 0;
540}
541
542yasm_section *
543yasm_cv__generate_symline(yasm_object *object, yasm_linemap *linemap,
544 yasm_errwarns *errwarns)
545{
546 yasm_dbgfmt_cv *dbgfmt_cv = (yasm_dbgfmt_cv *)object->dbgfmt;
547 cv_line_info info;
548 int new;
549 size_t i;
550 cv8_symhead *head;
551 cv8_lineinfo *li;
552 yasm_bytecode *bc;
553 unsigned long off;
554
555 /* Generate filenames based on linemap */
556 yasm_linemap_traverse_filenames(linemap, dbgfmt_cv,
557 cv_generate_filename);
558
559 info.object = object;
560 info.dbgfmt_cv = dbgfmt_cv;
561 info.linemap = linemap;
562 info.errwarns = errwarns;
563 info.debug_symline =
564 yasm_object_get_general(object, ".debug$S", 1, 0, 0, &new, 0);
565 info.num_lineinfos = 0;
566 STAILQ_INIT(&info.cv8_lineinfos);
567 info.cv8_cur_li = NULL;
568 info.cv8_cur_ls = NULL;
569
570 /* source filenames string table */
571 head = cv8_add_symhead(info.debug_symline, CV8_FILE_STRTAB, 1);
572 cv_append_str(info.debug_symline, "");
573 off = 1;
574 for (i=0; i<dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size; i++) {
575 if (!dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].pathname) {
576 yasm_error_set(YASM_ERROR_GENERAL,
577 N_("codeview file number %d unassigned"), i+1);
578 yasm_errwarn_propagate(errwarns, 0);
579 continue;
580 }
581 bc = cv_append_str(info.debug_symline,
582 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].pathname);
583 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].str_off = off;
584 off += bc->len;
585 }
586 cv8_set_symhead_end(head, yasm_section_bcs_last(info.debug_symline));
587
588 /* Align 4 */
589 bc = yasm_bc_create_align
590 (yasm_expr_create_ident(yasm_expr_int(yasm_intnum_create_uint(4)), 0),
591 NULL, NULL, NULL, 0);
592 yasm_bc_finalize(bc, yasm_cv__append_bc(info.debug_symline, bc));
593 yasm_bc_calc_len(bc, NULL, NULL);
594
595 /* source file info table */
596 head = cv8_add_symhead(info.debug_symline, CV8_FILE_INFO, 0);
597 off = 0;
598 for (i=0; i<dbgfmt_cv->filenames_size; i++) {
599 if (!dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].pathname)
600 continue;
601 bc = cv8_add_fileinfo(info.debug_symline, &dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i]);
602 dbgfmt_cv->filenames[i].info_off = off;
603 off += bc->len;
604 }
605 cv8_set_symhead_end(head, yasm_section_bcs_last(info.debug_symline));
606
607 /* Already aligned 4 */
608
609 /* Generate line numbers for sections */
610 yasm_object_sections_traverse(object, (void *)&info,
611 cv_generate_line_section);
612
613 /* Output line numbers for sections */
614 head = NULL;
615 STAILQ_FOREACH(li, &info.cv8_lineinfos, link) {
616 if (li->first_in_sect) {
617 if (head)
618 cv8_set_symhead_end(head, yasm_section_bcs_last(info.debug_symline));
619 head = cv8_add_symhead(info.debug_symline, CV8_LINE_NUMS, 0);
620 }
621 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv8_lineinfo_bc_callback, li, 0);
622 bc->len = (li->first_in_sect ? 24 : 12) + li->num_linenums*8;
623 yasm_cv__append_bc(info.debug_symline, bc);
624 }
625 if (head)
626 cv8_set_symhead_end(head, yasm_section_bcs_last(info.debug_symline));
627
628 /* Already aligned 4 */
629
630 /* Output debugging symbols */
631 head = cv8_add_symhead(info.debug_symline, CV8_DEBUG_SYMS, 0);
632 /* add object and compile flag first */
633 cv8_add_sym_objname(info.debug_symline,
634 yasm__abspath(object->obj_filename));
635 if (getenv("YASM_TEST_SUITE"))
636 cv8_add_sym_compile(object, info.debug_symline,
637 yasm__xstrdup("yasm HEAD"));
638 else
639 cv8_add_sym_compile(object, info.debug_symline,
640 yasm__xstrdup(PACKAGE_STRING));
641 /* then iterate through symbol table */
642 yasm_symtab_traverse(object->symtab, &info, cv_generate_sym);
643 cv8_set_symhead_end(head, yasm_section_bcs_last(info.debug_symline));
644
645 /* Align 4 at end */
646 bc = yasm_bc_create_align
647 (yasm_expr_create_ident(yasm_expr_int(yasm_intnum_create_uint(4)), 0),
648 NULL, NULL, NULL, 0);
649 yasm_bc_finalize(bc, yasm_cv__append_bc(info.debug_symline, bc));
650 yasm_bc_calc_len(bc, NULL, NULL);
651
652 return info.debug_symline;
653}
654
655static void
656cv_out_sym(yasm_symrec *sym, unsigned long off, yasm_bytecode *bc,
657 unsigned char **bufp, void *d, yasm_output_value_func output_value)
658{
659 yasm_value val;
660
661 /* sym in its section */
662 yasm_value_init_sym(&val, sym, 32);
663 val.section_rel = 1;
664 output_value(&val, *bufp, 4, off, bc, 0, d);
665 *bufp += 4;
666
667 /* section index */
668 yasm_value_init_sym(&val, sym, 16);
669 val.seg_of = 1;
670 output_value(&val, *bufp, 2, off+4, bc, 0, d);
671 *bufp += 2;
672}

674static cv8_symhead *
675cv8_add_symhead(yasm_section *sect, unsigned long type, int first)
676{
677 cv8_symhead *head;
678 yasm_bytecode *bc;
679
680 head = yasm_xmalloc(sizeof(cv8_symhead));
681 head->type = type;
682 head->first = first;
683 head->start_prevbc = yasm_section_bcs_last(sect);
684
685 bc = yasm_bc_create_common(&cv8_symhead_bc_callback, head, 0);
686 if (first)
687 bc->len = 12;
688 else
689 bc->len = 8;
690
691 head->end_prevbc = bc;
692 yasm_cv__append_bc(sect, bc);
693 return head;
694}

723static int
724cv8_symhead_bc_tobytes(yasm_bytecode *bc, unsigned char **bufp,
725 unsigned char *bufstart, void *d,
726 yasm_output_value_func output_value,
727 yasm_output_reloc_func output_reloc)
728{
729 yasm_object *object = yasm_section_get_object(bc->section);
730 cv8_symhead *head = (cv8_symhead *)bc->contents;
731 unsigned char *buf = *bufp;
732 yasm_intnum *intn, *cval;
733
734 cval = yasm_intnum_create_uint(4);
735 /* Output "version" if first */
736 if (head->first) {
737 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
738 buf += 4;
739 }
740
741 /* Type contained - 4 bytes */
742 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, head->type);
743 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
744 buf += 4;
745
746 /* Total length of info (following this field) - 4 bytes */
747 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, bc->len);
748 intn = yasm_calc_bc_dist(head->start_prevbc, head->end_prevbc);
749 yasm_intnum_calc(intn, YASM_EXPR_SUB, cval);
750 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, intn, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
751 buf += 4;
752 yasm_intnum_destroy(intn);
753
754 *bufp = buf;
755
756 yasm_intnum_destroy(cval);
757 return 0;
758}

797static int
798cv8_fileinfo_bc_tobytes(yasm_bytecode *bc, unsigned char **bufp,
799 unsigned char *bufstart, void *d,
800 yasm_output_value_func output_value,
801 yasm_output_reloc_func output_reloc)
802{
803 yasm_object *object = yasm_section_get_object(bc->section);
804 cv8_fileinfo *fi = (cv8_fileinfo *)bc->contents;
805 unsigned char *buf = *bufp;
806 yasm_intnum *cval;
807 int i;
808
809 /* Offset in filename string table */
810 cval = yasm_intnum_create_uint(fi->fn->str_off);
811 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
812 buf += 4;
813
814 /* Checksum type/length */
815 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, 0x0110);
816 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 2, 16, 0, bc, 0);
817 buf += 2;
818
819 /* Checksum */
820 for (i=0; i<16; i++)
821 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, fi->fn->digest[i]);
822
823 /* Pad */
824 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, 0);
825 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, 0);
826
827 *bufp = buf;
828
829 yasm_intnum_destroy(cval);
830 return 0;
831}

834cv8_lineinfo_bc_destroy(void *contents)

840 ls1 = STAILQ_FIRST(&li->linesets);
841 while (ls1) {

843 yasm_xfree(ls1);
844 ls1 = ls2;
845 }
846
847 yasm_xfree(contents);
848}

865static int
866cv8_lineinfo_bc_tobytes(yasm_bytecode *bc, unsigned char **bufp,
867 unsigned char *bufstart, void *d,
868 yasm_output_value_func output_value,
869 yasm_output_reloc_func output_reloc)
870{
871 yasm_object *object = yasm_section_get_object(bc->section);
872 cv8_lineinfo *li = (cv8_lineinfo *)bc->contents;
873 unsigned char *buf = *bufp;
874 yasm_intnum *cval;
875 unsigned long i;
876 cv8_lineset *ls;
877
878 if (li->first_in_sect) {
879 /* start offset and section */
880 cv_out_sym(li->sectsym, (unsigned long)(buf - bufstart), bc, &buf,
881 d, output_value);
882
883 /* Two bytes of pad/alignment */
884 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, 0);
885 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, 0);
886
887 /* Section length covered by line number info */
888 cval = yasm_calc_bc_dist(yasm_section_bcs_first(li->sect),
889 yasm_section_bcs_last(li->sect));
890 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
891 yasm_intnum_destroy(cval);
892 buf += 4;
893 }
894
895 /* Offset of source file in info table */
896 cval = yasm_intnum_create_uint(li->fn->info_off);
897 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
898 buf += 4;
899
900 /* Number of line number pairs */
901 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, li->num_linenums);
902 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
903 buf += 4;
904
905 /* Number of bytes of line number pairs + 12 (no, I don't know why) */
906 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, li->num_linenums*8+12);
907 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
908 buf += 4;
909
910 /* Offset / line number pairs */
911 i = 0;
912 STAILQ_FOREACH(ls, &li->linesets, link) {
913 unsigned long j;
914 for (j=0; i<li->num_linenums && j<126; i++, j++) {
915 /* offset in section */
916 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, ls->pairs[j].offset);
917 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
918 buf += 4;
919
920 /* line number in file */
921 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, ls->pairs[j].line);
922 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0, bc, 0);
923 buf += 4;
924 }
925 }
926
927 *bufp = buf;
928
929 yasm_intnum_destroy(cval);
930 return 0;
931}

933static unsigned long
934cv_sym_size(const cv_sym *cvs)
935{
936 const char *ch = cvs->format;
937 unsigned long len = 4; /* sym length and type */
938 unsigned long slen;
939 int arg = 0;
940
941 while (*ch) {
942 switch (*ch) {
943 case 'b':
944 len++;
945 arg++;
946 break;
947 case 'h':
948 len += 2;
949 arg++;
950 break;
951 case 'w':
952 len += 4;
953 arg++;
954 break;
955 case 'Y':
956 len += 6; /* XXX: will be 4 in 16-bit version */
957 arg++;
958 break;
959 case 'T':
960 len += 4; /* XXX: will be 2 in CV4 */
961 arg++;
962 break;
963 case 'S':
964 len += 1; /* XXX: is this 1 or 2? */
965 slen = (unsigned long)strlen((const char *)cvs->args[arg++].p);
966 len += slen <= 0xff ? slen : 0xff;
967 break;
968 case 'Z':
969 len +=
970 (unsigned long)strlen((const char *)cvs->args[arg++].p) + 1;
971 break;
972 default:
973 yasm_internal_error(N_("unknown sym format character"));
974 }
975 ch++;
976 }
977
978 return len;
979}

981static void
982cv_sym_bc_destroy(void *contents)
983{
984 cv_sym *cvs = (cv_sym *)contents;
985 const char *ch = cvs->format;
986 int arg = 0;
987
988 while (*ch) {
989 switch (*ch) {
990 case 'b':
991 case 'h':
992 case 'w':
993 case 'Y':
994 case 'T':
995 arg++;
996 break; /* nothing to destroy */
997 case 'S':
998 case 'Z':
999 yasm_xfree(cvs->args[arg++].p);
1000 break;
1001 default:
1002 yasm_internal_error(N_("unknown sym format character"));
1003 }
1004 ch++;
1005 }
1006
1007 yasm_xfree(contents);
1008}

1025static int
1026cv_sym_bc_tobytes(yasm_bytecode *bc, unsigned char **bufp,
1027 unsigned char *bufstart, void *d,
1028 yasm_output_value_func output_value,
1029 yasm_output_reloc_func output_reloc)
1030{
1031 yasm_object *object = yasm_section_get_object(bc->section);
1032 cv_sym *cvs = (cv_sym *)bc->contents;
1033 unsigned char *buf = *bufp;
1034 yasm_intnum *cval;
1035 const char *ch = cvs->format;
1036 size_t len;
1037 int arg = 0;
1038
1039 /* Total length of record (following this field) - 2 bytes */
1040 cval = yasm_intnum_create_uint(bc->len-2);
1041 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 2, 16, 0, bc, 1);
1042 buf += 2;
1043
1044 /* Type contained - 2 bytes */
1045 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, cvs->type);
1046 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 2, 16, 0, bc, 0);
1047 buf += 2;
1048
1049 while (*ch) {
1050 switch (*ch) {
1051 case 'b':
1052 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, cvs->args[arg].i);
1053 arg++;
1054 break;
1055 case 'h':
1056 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, cvs->args[arg++].i);
1057 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 2, 16, 0,
1058 bc, 0);
1059 buf += 2;
1060 break;
1061 case 'w':
1062 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, cvs->args[arg++].i);
1063 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0,
1064 bc, 0);
1065 buf += 4;
1066 break;
1067 case 'Y':
1068 cv_out_sym((yasm_symrec *)cvs->args[arg++].p,
1069 (unsigned long)(buf-bufstart), bc, &buf, d,
1070 output_value);
1071 break;
1072 case 'T':
1073 yasm_intnum_set_uint(cval, cvs->args[arg++].i);
1074 yasm_arch_intnum_tobytes(object->arch, cval, buf, 4, 32, 0,
1075 bc, 0);
1076 buf += 4; /* XXX: will be 2 in CV4 */
1077 break;
1078 case 'S':
1079 len = strlen((char *)cvs->args[arg].p);
1080 len = len <= 0xff ? len : 0xff;
1081 YASM_WRITE_8(buf, len);
1082 memcpy(buf, (char *)cvs->args[arg].p, len);
1083 buf += len;
1084 arg++;
1085 break;
1086 case 'Z':
1087 len = strlen((char *)cvs->args[arg].p)+1;
1088 memcpy(buf, (char *)cvs->args[arg].p, len);
1089 buf += len;
1090 arg++;
1091 break;
1092 default:
1093 yasm_internal_error(N_("unknown leaf format character"));
1094 }
1095 ch++;
1096 }
1097
1098 *bufp = buf;
1099
1100 yasm_intnum_destroy(cval);
1101 return 0;
1102}
